    <id>https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-q-a/re-sap-build-apps-delete-item-persistent-storage/qaq-p/13982356/comment-id/4898601#M4898601</id>
    <title>Re: SAP Build Apps - Delete Item Persistent Storage</title>
    <updated>2025-01-10T09:29:57.532000+01:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Dan_Wroblewski</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/72</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;An ID is generated for every record and you must use this ID to identify the record you want to delete.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;For example, I have a UI that lets me create a record with a random UUID, and a delete button to delete that particular record.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Dan_Wroblewski_1-1736497433276.png" style="width: 981px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/210491iEDCB18B383B89E7F/image-dimensions/981x254?v=v2" width="981" height="254" role="button" title="Dan_Wroblewski_1-1736497433276.png" alt="Dan_Wroblewski_1-1736497433276.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;I have an on-device storage entity with 2 fields plus the default ID field.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Dan_Wroblewski_0-1736497416719.png" style="width: 1004px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/210490i7B87A4E436378007/image-dimensions/1004x390?v=v2" width="1004" height="390" role="button" title="Dan_Wroblewski_0-1736497416719.png" alt="Dan_Wroblewski_0-1736497416719.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;H3 id="toc-hId-1208418338"&gt;The set logic&lt;/H3&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Dan_Wroblewski_2-1736497484760.png" style="width: 864px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/210495iC321586845188903/image-dimensions/864x95?v=v2" width="864" height="95" role="button" title="Dan_Wroblewski_2-1736497484760.png" alt="Dan_Wroblewski_2-1736497484760.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;The Create Record is just setting the name field to a random UUID.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Dan_Wroblewski_3-1736497544024.png" style="width: 904px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/210496i93620376B42C37E7/image-dimensions/904x174?v=v2" width="904" height="174" role="button" title="Dan_Wroblewski_3-1736497544024.png" alt="Dan_Wroblewski_3-1736497544024.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;H3 id="toc-hId-1011904833"&gt;The delete logic&amp;nbsp;&lt;/H3&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Dan_Wroblewski_4-1736497612365.png" style="width: 868px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/210497i479AC28F172F8F52/image-dimensions/868x102?v=v2" width="868" height="102" role="button" title="Dan_Wroblewski_4-1736497612365.png" alt="Dan_Wroblewski_4-1736497612365.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;The Delete Record only has data resource and ID fields.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Dan_Wroblewski_5-1736497657671.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/210498i3E87E19CC083555F/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Dan_Wroblewski_5-1736497657671.png" alt="Dan_Wroblewski_5-1736497657671.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;And for the ID I select Data Item in Repeat and select the ID field.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Dan_Wroblewski_6-1736497734948.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/210499iB00EC352C78A63CC/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Dan_Wroblewski_6-1736497734948.png" alt="Dan_Wroblewski_6-1736497734948.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;P.S.: Strangely, it is permitted to delete the ID field. Then it seems you could not select a specific row but you'd have select a collection and then add your own logic to find the record you want.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-q-a/re-sap-build-apps-delete-item-persistent-storage/qaq-p/13982356/comment-id/4898601#M4898601"/>
    <published>2025-01-10T09:29:57.532000+01:00</published>
